<div id="poem-top" class="tab-content active">
	<h1>The Mower</h1>
</div>
<div id="about-top" class="tab-content">
	<div class="tabs-poem">
		<h1><a href="#poem" class="blue">The Mower</a></h1>
	</div>
</div>

<span class="author">By <a href="/bio/philip-larkin"> Philip  Larkin</a> <span class="birthyear">1922&ndash;1985</span></span>
	<span class='fullname_search'>Philip Larkin</span>
	
	
		
	







	<div id="poem" class="tab-content active">

		
				<div class="poem">
					
					<div style='text-indent: -1em; padding-left: 1em;'>The mower stalled, twice; kneeling, I found&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>
<div style='text-indent: -1em; padding-left: 1em;'>A hedgehog jammed up against the blades,&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>
<div style='text-indent: -1em; padding-left: 1em;'>Killed. It had been in the long grass. </div>
<br/>
<div style='text-indent: -1em; padding-left: 1em;'>I had seen it before, and even fed it, once.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>
<div style='text-indent: -1em; padding-left: 1em;'>Now I had mauled its unobtrusive world&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>
<div style='text-indent: -1em; padding-left: 1em;'>Unmendably. Burial was no help: </div>
<br/>
<div style='text-indent: -1em; padding-left: 1em;'>Next morning I got up and it did not. </div>
<div style='text-indent: -1em; padding-left: 1em;'>The first day after a death, the new absence&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>
<div style='text-indent: -1em; padding-left: 1em;'>Is always the same; we should be careful </div>
<br/>
<div style='text-indent: -1em; padding-left: 1em;'>Of each other, we should be kind&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>
<div style='text-indent: -1em; padding-left: 1em;'>While there is still time.</div>
				</div>
			
		
		
			<div class="credit">
					
					
					<p>
					Philip Larkin, &ldquo;The Mower&rdquo; from <em>Collected Poems.</em> Used by permission of The Society of Authors as the Literary Representative of the Estate of Philip Larkin.<br/><br/>
					
						<div class="booktip" style="display:none;" id="book_tip_571153860"></div>
						Source: <em id="source_571153860">Collected Poems</em> (Farrar Straus and Giroux, 2001)</em>
					
				</p>
			</div>
		

	


		<div class="section">
			<div class="divider"></div>
			<div class="right backtotop"><a href="#" class="backtotop">back to top</a></div>
		</div>

		
